      <div class=" clearFloats bigBox"><div class="h2Container gradientHeaderContainer"><h2 class="brownBackground"><a href="/work/quotes/28898746-dolmens-in-the-blue-mountain">Quotes from Dolmens in the Bl...</a></h2></div><div class="bigBoxBody"><div class="bigBoxContent containerWithHeaderContent">
